i" title="">马里</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/asia-pacific/myanmar" title="">缅甸</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/south-sudan" title="">南苏丹</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/nigeria" title="">尼日利亚</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/somalia" title="">索马里</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/syria" title="">叙利亚</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/yemen" title="">也门</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/iraq" title="">伊拉克</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/israel-and-occupied-territories" title="">以色列及被占领土</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/europe-central-asia/ukraine" title="">乌克兰</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/lake-chad" title="">乍得湖</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/asia-pacific/china" title="">中国</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/central-african-republic" title="">中非共和国</a></li></ul></div><div class="col-sm-4"><h5>主题</h5><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons/chemical-biological-weapons" title="">化学和生物武器</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/children" title="">儿童</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/visiting-detainees" title="">探视被拘留者</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/migrants" title="">移民</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons/ihl-and-new-technologies" title="">新科技与国际人道法</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons/nuclear-weapons" title="">核武器</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/occupation" title="">占领</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/refugees-displaced-persons" title="">国内流离失所者</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/respect-ihl" title="">遵守国际人道法</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/security-detention" title="">出于安全理由的拘留</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/sexual-violence" title="">性暴力</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism" title="">恐怖主义</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="visible-sm visible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law" selected="selected">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr/guerre-et-droit">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es/guerra-y-derecho">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt/guerra-e-o-direito">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar/war-and-law">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru/war-and-law">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de/krieg-recht">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">其他</option> </select></div></div></div></div> </header></div> <nav class="navbar navbar--main clearfix js_navbar" id="main-menu" role="navigation"><div class="container"><div class="nav-sub"> <button type="button" class="nav-toggle i-menu pull-left js_toggle" data-target=".navbar--main"> <span class="sr-only">展开导航</span> </button><div class="pull-right"><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-c