ontact" title="">联系我们</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-what nav-link-main-container"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do" class="nav-link-main">工作内容</a><div class="nav-submenu"> <a class="nav-link-sub-toggle i-arrow-left js_toggle visible-sm visible-xs" data-target=".nav-main">返回</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do" class="nav-link-spot i-arrow-right-after">概述 工作内容</a><div class=" nav-split"><ul><li><h5 class="h5">活动</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/ensuring-economic-security" title="">经济安全</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/restoring-family-links" title="">重建家庭联系</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/water-habitat" title="">供水与住所</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/access-education" title="">教育机会</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/health" title="">医疗卫生 </a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/sexual-violence" title="">应对性暴力</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/forensic-science" title="">法医学与人道行动</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/mine-action" title="">反地雷行动</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/building-respect-ihl" title="">促进遵守法律 </a></li></ul></li><li><h5 class="h5">我们帮助的人</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/civilians" title="">平民</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/women" title="">妇女</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/children" title="">儿童</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/visiting-detainees" title="">被拘留者</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/refugees-displaced-persons" title="">国内流离失所者</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/migrants" title="">移民、难民和寻求避难者</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/disability" title="">残障人士</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/missing-persons" title="">失踪人员</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-where nav-link-main-container"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work" class="nav-link-main">工作地区</a><div class="nav-submenu"> <a class="nav-link-sub-toggle i-arrow-left js_toggle visible-sm visible-xs" data-target=".nav-main">返回</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work" class="nav-link-spot i-arrow-right-after">概述 工作地区</a><div class=" nav-split"><ul><li><h5 class="h5">重要行动</h5><ul><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/democratic-republic-congo">刚果民主共和国</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/asia-pacific/myanmar">缅甸</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/south-sudan">南苏丹</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/somalia">索马里</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/syria">叙利亚</a></li></ul></li></ul><ul><li><h5 class="h5 country-col-2">&nbsp;</h5><ul><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/yemen">也门</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/middle-east/iraq">伊拉克</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/lake-chad">乍得湖</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/africa/central-african-republic">中非共和国</a></li><li><a class="nav-link-sub" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work/asia-pacific/china">中国</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-war nav-link-main-container"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law" class="nav-link-main">战争与法律</a><div class="nav-submenu"> <a class="nav-link-sub-toggle i-arrow-left js_toggle visible-sm visible-xs" data-target=".nav-main">返回</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law" class="nav-link-spot i-arrow