www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/planned-giving" title="">有计划捐助</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container pull-right hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate" class="bg-red nav-link-main">捐款</a></div></div></div></div> </nav></div><div class="region region-content"><div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system"><div class="content"> <section class="clearfix breadcrumb-wrapper theme-brown"><div class="container"><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="i-arrow-right-after"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh">主页</a></li><li class="active js_toggle i-arrow-up" data-target=".breadcrumb-wrapper">战争与法律</li></ol></div></section><section class="section-hero theme-brown"><div class="container"><h1 class="h1 font-xs-40 font-md-60">战争与法律</h1><p class="font-xs-18 font-md-24 sans-serif"><p>国际人道法是旨在出于人道原因限制武装冲突影响的一系列规则。它保护未参与或不再参与武装冲突的人，并限制作战方法和手段。</p></p></div></section><section class="clearfix theme-brown topic-theme-new banner-list" data-section="0"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/treaties-customary-law/geneva-conventions" ><img class="js_img border-bottom" src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_banner_wide/public/topic-theme/banner_list/geneva-convention-commentaries-2016_1.jpg?itok=8PywjQB6" data-src-phone="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/geneva-convention-commentaries-2016_1.jpg?itok=nDR93atB" data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_banner_wide/public/topic-theme/banner_list/geneva-convention-commentaries-2016_1.jpg?itok=8PywjQB6" alt="日内瓦公约" class="border-bottom" /><div class="caption background-gradient"><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-20 font-md-24 font-lg-32 i-arrow-right-after">日内瓦公约</div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/people-on-war" ><img class="js_img border-bottom" src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/iraq-war-fighting-destruction_2.jpg?itok=JdCq0Oui" data-src-phone="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/iraq-war-fighting-destruction_2.jpg?itok=JdCq0Oui" data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/iraq-war-fighting-destruction_2.jpg?itok=JdCq0Oui" alt="2016年“战争与人”调查" class="border-bottom" /><div class="caption background-gradient"><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-20 font-md-24 font-lg-32 i-arrow-right-after">2016年“战争与人”调查</div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/the-rules-of-war" ><img class="js_img border-bottom" src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/vaincre-a-tout-prix-thumnail_1_1.jpg?itok=PgpSA8b-" data-src-phone="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/vaincre-a-tout-prix-thumnail_1_1.jpg?itok=PgpSA8b-" data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/donation_operation_text_block/public/topic-theme/banner_list/vaincre-a-tout-prix-thumnail_1_1.jpg?itok=PgpSA8b-" alt="不计后果的胜利不是真正的胜利" class="border-bottom" /><div class="caption background-gradient"><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-20 font-md-24 font-lg-32 i-arrow-right-after">不计后果的胜利不是真正的胜利</div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-type="war_and_law_db" class="clearfix theme-brown topic-theme-new" data-section="1"><div class="page-header "><h2>国际人道法的来源</h2></div><div class="container js_equal-col-height" data-offset-element=".block"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-6 js_col"><div class="block"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/treaties-customary-law" class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 title i-arrow-right-after">国际人道法条约 </a><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>国际人道法的基础是一系列条约，尤其是1949年日内瓦公约及其附加议定书，以及一系列其他文件。</p><p><a href="https://ihl-databases.icrc.org/ihl" target="_blank">条约、缔约国和评注数据库</a></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 js_col"><div class="block"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/treaties-customary-law/customary-law" class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 title i-arrow-right-after">习惯国际人道法 </a><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>习惯国际法由"经接受为法律的一般实践"所形成的规则组成，这些规则在条约法之外独立存在。</p><p><a href="https://ihl-databases.icrc.org/customary-ihl/eng/docs/home" target="_blank">习惯国际人道法数据库</a></p></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></section><section class="clearfix bg-brown theme-brown"><div class="container vspace-small center-content"><div class="row"> <label for="ihl-search" class="h4 color-white-3 font-sans-serif margin-right no-margin-top">检索所有国际人道法数据库</label><form class="inline" method="get" action="https://ihl-databases.icrc.org/applic/ihl/ihl-search.nsf/xsearch.xsp" target="_blank"> <input type="hidden" name="lang" value="EN"/> <input type="search" name="ftsearch" id="ihl-search"/> <button class="small-margin-left btn">搜索</button></form></div></div></section><section data-type="item_list" class="clearfix theme-brown topic-theme-new" data-section="2"><div class="page-header "><h2>议题</h2></div><div class="container js_equal-col-height" data-offset-element=".block"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/challenges-ihl_0_2.jpg?itok=Fn9eS4YL" alt="当前有关国际人道法的辩论 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">当前有关国际人道法的辩论</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>理解并应对当代冲突给国际人道法带来的挑战。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/participation-hostilities">直接参加敌对行动</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism">恐怖主义</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons/ihl-and-new-technologies">新科技与国际人道法</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/protection_3.jpg?itok=lHt1PN1_" alt="受保护的人 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">受保护的人</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>国际人道法在武装冲突期间为大范围的人员和物品提供保护。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/civilians">平民</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/wounded-sick-and-shipwrecked">伤者、病者和遇船难者</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/prisoners-war-detainees">战俘与被拘留者</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/explosive-weapons-in-populated-area-gaza_3.jpg?itok=RIyggllp" alt="武器 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">武器</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>国际人道法规制武器的选择，并禁止或限制使用某些武器。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/explosive-weapons-populated-areas">在人口稠密地区使用爆炸性武器</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons/nuclear-weapons">核武器</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons/new-weapons">新武器的审查</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/conduct-of-hostilities_3.jpg?itok=Ys-_kZGF" alt="敌对行为 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">敌对行为</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>国际法规制作战方法与手段，目的是在合法军事目标与减轻人类（尤其是平民）苦难的人道目标之间寻求平衡。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities/methods-means-warfare">作战方法和手段</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities/cyber-warfare">网络战</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities/cultural-property">文化财产</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/emblem"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/emblems_3.jpg?itok=1BA_7ry_" alt="标志的使用 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">标志的使用</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>红十字、红新月和红水晶标志在武装冲突中为军队医疗服务部门和救济工作者提供保护。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/publication/0876-emblems-humanity">人道标志</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/emblem">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/international-criminal-jurisdiction"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/icc_3.jpg?itok=tQQXQnfy" alt="违反国际人道法 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">违反国际人道法</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>当违反国际人道法的行为发生，各国有义务惩治犯罪者。因此国内法院在国际人道法的执行方面发挥着重要作用。除了国内司法之外，违法国际人道法的行为还可以通过各个国际刑事法庭进行追诉。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/international-criminal-jurisdiction">国际刑事法庭</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/criminal-repression-serious-ihl-violations-information-kit">国内法院</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/international-humanitarian-fact-finding-commission-facsheet">其他机制</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/international-criminal-jurisdiction">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-domestic-law"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/domestic-law-2_2.jpg?itok=CONmE6jy" alt="国内法与国际人道法 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">国内法与国际人道法</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>国际人道法条约若要获得全球认可，所有国家都必须通过批准或加入条约对其予以采纳。之后，各国必须颁布国家立法并采取切实措施来保证国际人道法规则完全有效。红十字国际委员会的国际人道法咨询服务处可以通过提供援助和文献资料来给予帮助。</p><p><a href="https://ihl-databases.icrc.org/ihl-nat" target="_blank">红十字国际委员会国内实施数据库</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-domestic-law/national-committees">国家委员会</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-domestic-law/documentation">专题文件</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-domestic-law">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-other-legal-regimes"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/refugees_3.jpg?itok=5qADwNmj" alt="与国际人道法相关的法律体系 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">与国际人道法相关的法律体系</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>在武装冲突中，国际人道法和其他法律部门互为补充。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-other-legal-regmies/ihl-human-rights">人权法</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons/refugees-displaced-persons">难民法</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-other-legal-regmies/jus-in-bello-jus-ad-bellum">战时法</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-other-legal-regimes">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/strengthening-ihl"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/strengthening-ihl_2.jpg?itok=DtZrhtrN" alt="加强国际人道法 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">加强国际人道法</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>为了使国际人道法有效地规制各交战方的行为，不仅需要制定充分的规则，还需要各方切实遵守这些规则。</p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/detention-non-international-armed-conflict-icrcs-work-strengthening-legal-protection-0">加强国际人道法对被拘留者的保护</a></p><p><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/strengthening-compliance-international-humanitarian-law-ihl-work-icrc-and-swiss-government">加强对国际人道法的遵守</a></p><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/strengthening-ihl">查看全部</a></p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-type="publication_list" class="clearfix theme-brown topic-theme-new" data-section="3"><div class="page-header "><h2>出版物推荐</h2></div><div class="container js_equal-col-height" data-offset-element=".block"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-6 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="col-md-4"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/doc/resources/documents/publication/p0739.htm"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/review_cover/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/md_law-protect-in-war.jpg?itok=ocqv7Z-4" alt="战争中的法律保护 " class="border-bottom"></a></div></div><div class="col-md-8"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/doc/resources/documents/publication/p0739.htm" class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 title i-arrow-right-after">战争中的法律保护 </a><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>关于国际人道法当代实践的案例、文件与教学资料。</p><p><br />另见：<a href="https://casebook.icrc.org/">英文版</a></p></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="col-md-4"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/international-review"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/review_cover/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/894-cover.jpg?itok=UHNkC4KQ" alt="红十字国际评论 " class="border-bottom"></a></div></div><div class="col-md-8"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/international-review" class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 title i-arrow-right-after">红十字国际评论 </a><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>《红十字国际评论》创刊于1869年，其年度文选的中文版由红十字国际委员会东亚地区代表处与中国法律出版社合作出版。</p></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="col-md-4"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/updated-commentaries-first-geneva-convention"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/review_cover/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/geneva-commentaries-publications_1.jpg?itok=xyAplAT9" alt="日内瓦第一公约评注 " class="border-bottom"></a></div></div><div class="col-md-8"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/updated-commentaries-first-geneva-convention" class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 title i-arrow-right-after">日内瓦第一公约评注 </a><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>在20世纪50年代，红十字国际委员会出版了一套《日内瓦公约评注》。基于自那时起法律与实践方面的新进展（包括对各国对《公约》的普遍遵守）红十字国际委员会委托编写了一套新版评注，以体现当代对《日内瓦公约》的解读。</p></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-12 view-all-publications"><a href="https://shop.icrc.org/publications/international-humanitarian-law.html" target="_blank" class="btn i-arrow-right-after">查阅所有出版物</a><br /><br /><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/library-and-research-services" class="btn i-arrow-right-after">资料查阅与研究服务</a><br /><span class="font-xs-12">资料查阅与研究服务页面可检索超过14万<br />份关于国际人道法与红十字国际委员会工作的文件。</span></div></div></div></section><section data-type="item_list" class="clearfix theme-brown topic-theme-new" data-section="4"><div class="page-header "><h2>服务与资源</h2></div><div class="container js_equal-col-height" data-offset-element=".block"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/icrc-advisory-services-international-humanitarian-law"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/icrc-advisory-services-eng_1.png?itok=sx1Dp79a" alt="法律咨询服务处 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">法律咨询服务处</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>国际人道法咨询服务处是红十字国际委员会的一个专门机构，协助各国政府在国家层面实施国际人道法。</p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/building-respect-ihl/education-outreach"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/ehl_2.jpg?itok=wiFSC0Fg" alt="教授与学习国际人道法 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">教授与学习国际人道法</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>红十字国际委员会支持人道法和人道原则的教学工作，旨在影响未来的决策者和舆论领袖。</p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 js_col"><div class="block"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/law-and-policy"><img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_highlight/public/field-collections/topic-theme-section-1-list/image/law-and-policy_0_0.jpg?itok=2Z_SsxIK" alt="法律与政策论坛 " class="border-bottom"><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-20 i-arrow-right-after">法律与政策论坛</p></div></a></div><div class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18 text"><p>丰富的资源将国际人道法与指导人道行动的政策连接起来。</p></div><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><footer class="clear"> <nav class="footer-nav clear"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-3"><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm"><h2>红十字国际委员会的工作</h2><div><p>红十字国际委员会帮助受武装冲突影响的人群，并促进对国际人道法的遵守。进一步了解我们的<a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do">工作内容</a>和<a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/who-we-are">组织介绍</a>。</p></div></div><div class="hidden-md hidden-lg"><h2>订阅红十字国际委员会简报</h2><div><form action="https://www.icrc.org/zh/newsletter" method="get" novalidate="novalidate" class="footer-newsletter-form"> <button type="submit">订阅</button><div class="input-wrapper"> <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="你的电子邮件"></div></form></div></div></div><div class="col-md-2"><h2>栏目</h2><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm"><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/who-we-are">组织介绍</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do">工作内容</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work">工作地区</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law">战争与法律</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us">支持我们</a></li></ul></div><div class="hidden-md hidden-lg"><div class="footer-dropdown"> <button>...<span class="button-icon i-arrow-down"></span></button><div class="footer-dropdown-content"><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/who-we-are">组织介绍</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do">工作内容</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/where-we-work">工作地区</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law">战争与法律</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us">支持我们</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="col-md-3"><h2>快速链接</h2><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm"><ul><li> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh">主页</a></li><li> <a href="https:/